                <h1>Where Do Pandas Live? Discover Their Natural Habitat!</h1>
                <p>Pandas primarily inhabit the mountain ranges of central China, particularly in Sichuan, Shaanxi, and Gansu provinces. They thrive in bamboo forests, which provide their main food source. Due to habitat loss and fragmentation, conservation efforts are crucial to protect these magnificent creatures and their natural environments.</p>
